text: Laurent Cathala (born September 21, 1945) is the current mayor of Créteil and is a former member of the National Assembly of France. He represented the Val- de-Marne department, and is a member of the Socialiste, radical, citoyen et divers gauche. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Socialist Party (France) politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Mayors of places in Île-de-France Category:Politicians from Occitanie
title: Laurent Cathala
